Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,およそ遠しとされしもの　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:13.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見慣れた動植物とは　まるで違うと　おぼしきモノ達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:20.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヒトは古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,鳥の声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体 どこから…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,足元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あなたも貝殻を集めてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ あげる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あなた崖の上に住んでる子でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,向こうはあまり貝殻ないものね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あ…ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ あなた ちゃんとしゃべれるのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ もっと貝のあるところ教えてあげようか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:57.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,知ってる？ 貝の中にも波の音 鳴ってるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,またおいでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また遊ぼうね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミナ ミナ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつを里で米と交換してきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,浜の連中とは口聞くんじゃねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あのう ちょいといいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何者だ　あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,通りすがりの蟲師で 銀古ってんですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここらの海に凶兆が出てるんで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,知らせたほうがいいかと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,凶兆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,浜に誰もいない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,少しだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,綺麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これも波の音するかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,鳥の声？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:06:00.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ 凶兆と言っても まだ何が起こるかは分からんのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,確実近いうちに 何らかの厄災がある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:07.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,村中に備えを呼びかけといたほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,己の身は己で守る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,村は村だ 俺には関係ねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミナちゃん ミナちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？ ぼうっとして 大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家まで送って行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,シマちゃん 本当にこの子口聞けるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんにも言わないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当よ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何してる 帰るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして言うことが聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それもよりによってあの娘と
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの娘とは 二度と口を聞くなと言ったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした ちゃんと言ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「貝の唄」を聞いたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「貝の唄」とは言えど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,唄ってるのは貝殻の中に住む「蟲」でしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,宿借り鳥とか　囀り貝とか言いましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:39.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,普段は海上を飛び回り 藻屑なんかを喰ってるものなんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海で異変を察すると浜へ上がり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:47.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,貝の殻に閉じこもって 災いの去るのを待つんです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:55.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして 小さな声で鳴き続け 仲間を陸へ呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを耳の真近で聞いてしまうと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人は声の出し方を忘れてしまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,治す方法はあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:10.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何 毎日人の声聞いていれば じき思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,勝手なことをするからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,二度としたら許さんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:24.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ そういう事で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,問題は「災い」の方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,村の方には俺から伝えとくが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたらも気をつけたほうがいいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海で災い？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだそりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,高潮か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大嵐でも来るってのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ そのどっちの記録もある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,備えはしておいたほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,備えなら常にしている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:59.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海に出る時にゃいつだって何が起こるか分かんねぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,出来る限りの注意を払ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,忠告はありがてぇが 特別する事はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんならいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前ら明日も抜かるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,抜かるなっつったて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,明日も生け簀の魚の世話だしなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:27.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,暇だ 俺 海女漁のほうが好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:31.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう言うな 網元も考えあってのことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,養殖が旨く行きゃわしら網子を安全に養える
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もうあんな惨いことも起こらんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,惨いこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう 十年前になるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:51.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,網元の乗ってた舟で海女が鱶に喰われたろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,引き上げんが間に合わなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ ありゃ酷かった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海が血で真っ赤になって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その海女の旦那は それ切り網子をやめて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:11.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,娘と二人っきり崖の方で漁をしてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気持ちは分からんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:20.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,網元は先に自分の女房を引き上げたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺でもいざって時にゃそうするぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうさなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,網元が養殖に取り組み出したのはそれからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,網元の気持ちもよく分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,胸の痛いことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お帰り お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:56.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あのね 今日 浜でミナちゃんに会ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:11:00.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも ミナちゃんのお父さんが私と口聞いちゃいけないって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしてかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は何も気にしなくていいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は何も悪くはねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大変だ 鱶が出た
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前の女房が…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:05.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺が乗っていりゃ こんなことにはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:11.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,砂吉 あん時はどうしようもなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしようもない？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:21.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,他人に女房の命を預けた俺が悪かったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:22.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,帰ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これからは 己の身が己で守る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また数が増えたな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,貝が小さな声で鳴いている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,仲間のために
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,生きるために
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:42.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの娘 大したもんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ小せぇのに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと母親の代わりに潜ってきたんだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,可哀そうな気もするが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このことは誰にも言うんじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺にもしものことがあったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これがあればなんとかなる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰もお前を守っちゃくれねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分の身は自分で守るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:39.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:42.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,話があって来た
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:52.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,近いうち 海で災いがあると蟲師が言ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前たちも用心しとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたに言われる筋合はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が起こるか予測つかんか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海の異変を察するのはお前が一番長けていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,知ったことか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:20.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,砂吉よ 村じゃ この十年 海で一つの事故もなくやってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:26.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この先も 俺の目の前で誰一人死なせはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,村に戻って養殖を手伝っちゃくれんか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:37.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ようやく うまく育てくれるようになったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:41.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これでみんな安心して食っていけるようになる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:47.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,娘と二人だけで漁をしていってはいつかは危ない目に遭うぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それでいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前のことだ 許せないのは俺ばかりではないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いまだに自分を責めているなら もう止せ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:03.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前にはもっと大事なことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:08.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,娘の将来を思うなら 戻って来い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:20.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また来る くれぐれも用心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,歌が…止んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:53.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かった 念のため みんなを崖の上に避難させよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が光った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,魚があんなに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:17.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤潮だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんて…ことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:18:00.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どう逃げようとも 無駄だというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:09.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こればかりは どうしようもない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしようも　なかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ようやく赤潮も引いてきたな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:39.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが これで養殖もおしまいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ また裸一貫 海女やりゃいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ声は戻らんか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:57.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう少し大勢の人の声を聞かせたら いいんだと思うがね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 俺はこれで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:19.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙だな 赤潮は去ったのに まだ海へ戻らない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:26.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,災いはまだ 終わっていない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミナ ついて来い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,砂吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海女漁はまだ止せ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤潮の後は毒を持つ貝が出る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれなことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かってるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,後はこうしてやってくしかないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺もやめたほうがいいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,凶兆がまだ去っちゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ どうしろというんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:15.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,砂吉 お前だって海が元に戻るまでどう食いつなぐんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:23.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,開けてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミナの獲った真珠だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,みんなで分ければわずかだが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,売れば生活の足しにはなるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが こんな立派なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,犠牲が出るよりはましだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その代り 俺と娘をまたよろしく頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,無論だとも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その後 その近辺の浜で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:16.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,貝を食べたと思われる海鳥の骸が時折に見られた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:22.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,けれど結局 その村においては一人の犠牲も出ることはなかったという
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:47.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミナちゃん 早く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:49.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今行く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何見てたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでもないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:43.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,雪の下
